data.description: Updated Tokeland home with Views of Willapa Bay & River! This home is a must see with so much Character you will fall in love at first site! Well Built in 1917 & large with 2372 SF, 5 bed, 2 bath & views from the spacious master bedroom, cozy living room & dining! Kitchen has all new cabinets, floors, counters & stainless appliances. Wood Stove & new chimney will keep you warm! Detached shop, beautiful landscaping, fire pit & fully fenced. This is a must see with an excellent location & views!
data.whatILove: Beautiful Tokeland home, has so much character with a beautiful view plus beach access. Nice remodeled kitchen with beautiful stainless appliances and adjoining breakfast nook and computer station. Large living room with fireplace and many windows with a view! 5 bedrooms 2 bathrooms large 24x24 detached garage. lovely yard and located in the sunbelt known as Tokeland. You won't want to miss this one. Very Motivated Seller
